309
00:19:28.018 --> 00:19:29.077
What?

310
00:19:30.917 --> 00:19:32.887
Gosh, why those little...

311
00:19:33.587 --> 00:19:34.657
Forget it.

312
00:19:35.188 --> 00:19:37.218
I gave them a lesson already.

313
00:19:37.827 --> 00:19:38.887
How?

314
00:19:38.887 --> 00:19:40.587
I threw my cigarette...

315
00:19:40.728 --> 00:19:43.157
in Mr. Park's coffee cup like this.

316
00:19:44.867 --> 00:19:47.498
Those punks are driving me crazy.

317
00:19:48.137 --> 00:19:50.698
I'll earn a lot of money and buy your company for certain.

318
00:19:50.698 --> 00:19:52.768
And I'll give those darn employees...

319
00:19:53.137 --> 00:19:55.438
