347
00:21:40.377 --> 00:21:43.048
What? He supports the family?

348
00:21:43.778 --> 00:21:46.417
He gives me a tiny amount of living expenses,

349
00:21:46.518 --> 00:21:48.657
and he takes so much credit for it.

350
00:21:48.657 --> 00:21:50.458
Goodness, I can't stand this.

351
00:21:50.988 --> 00:21:54.627
- My life is so miserable. - Gosh.

352
00:22:21.857 --> 00:22:23.958
I'm taking my day off tomorrow.

353
00:22:27.458 --> 00:22:29.028
- Is that right? - Yes.

354
00:22:29.298 --> 00:22:33.028
Let me know your parents' house address, and I'll go there in time.

355
00:22:34.938 --> 00:22:37.738
Okay, I'll send you the address.

356
00:22:42.907 --> 00:22:44.008
By the way,

357
00:22:45.008 --> 00:22:47.008
I can't go there tomorrow.

358
00:22:47.377 --> 00:22:49.048
I know.

359
00:22:49.347 --> 00:22:51.188
You have to work.

360
00:22:53.587 --> 00:22:55.458
You went to our memorial service alone.

361
00:22:56.117 --> 00:22:58.857
So it's only right for me to go to your house alone too.

362
00:22:59.627 --> 00:23:02.698
I'll work there for six hours just like you did.

363
00:23:08.397 --> 00:23:12.107
Did you put the contract in your office?

364
00:23:13.938 --> 00:23:15.877
No, it's in my briefcase.

365
00:23:16.978 --> 00:23:20.008
Mr. Ma goes through my documents from time to time.

366
00:23:20.308 --> 00:23:21.847
So I thought it'd be safer this way.

367
00:23:23.048 --> 00:23:26.387
We'll be in trouble if Mr. Ma finds out about this.

368
00:23:26.788 --> 00:23:28.758
Right, that should never happen.

369
00:23:29.117 --> 00:23:31.728
Then it'll be only a matter of time Soo Ji finds out too.

370
00:23:32.958 --> 00:23:34.087
What?

371
00:23:35.357 --> 00:23:36.657
Didn't you know?

372
00:23:37.327 --> 00:23:40.298
Mr. Ma and Soo Ji are dating.

373
00:23:41.268 --> 00:23:42.367
They're dating?

374
00:23:42.998 --> 00:23:45.907
How did that happen?

375
00:23:45.907 --> 00:23:47.008
Tell me about it.

376
00:23:47.337 --> 00:23:50.137
Humans are such interesting beings.

377
00:23:51.407 --> 00:23:53.048
They don't look good together at all.

378
00:23:53.647 --> 00:23:55.647
But how can they be in a relationship?

379
00:23:59.117 --> 00:24:00.288
What is he talking about?

380
00:24:01.488 --> 00:24:03.087
We're married too.

381
00:24:18.167 --> 00:24:21.538
My girlfriend is braless?

382
00:24:26.607 --> 00:24:28.548
People would notice it for certain.

383
00:24:28.778 --> 00:24:31.617
You think they wouldn't, don't you? But they notice it right away.

384
00:24:32.488 --> 00:24:35.157
It's their fault to notice it, not mine.

385
00:24:35.357 --> 00:24:38.458
Of course, it's their fault. I'm sure about it, but...

386
00:24:40.688 --> 00:24:42.397
Tell me honestly. Have you...

387
00:24:42.397 --> 00:24:44.768
gone to work without wearing a bra before as well?

388
00:24:44.998 --> 00:24:46.097
Sometimes.

389
00:24:47.298 --> 00:24:49.538
I take it off when I work away and sometimes forget to wear it back on.

390
00:24:49.637 --> 00:24:50.907
My goodness.

391
00:24:51.667 --> 00:24:53.438
You're crazy.

392
00:24:53.837 --> 00:24:56.708
I would've gone naked if I really were crazy.

393
00:24:58.077 --> 00:25:01.548
Goodness.

394
00:25:02.877 --> 00:25:05.248
Do you really have to talk back to every single word I say?

395
00:25:05.587 --> 00:25:08.857
Understand me a little. I hate it.

396
00:25:09.317 --> 00:25:11.028
Why are you so angry?

397
00:25:12.558 --> 00:25:13.728
Soo Ji.

398
00:25:14.127 --> 00:25:16.097
Can't you feel my heart?

399
00:25:16.427 --> 00:25:19.367
My true worrying and loving heart?

400
00:25:20.028 --> 00:25:21.137
I'm not sure.

401
00:25:21.337 --> 00:25:24.308
Why do I feel like you're rationalizing yourself...

402
00:25:24.508 --> 00:25:26.208
and romanticizing your possessiveness with love?

403
00:25:26.438 --> 00:25:29.907
Why do you feel that way?

404
00:25:31.548 --> 00:25:33.748
This is different from our contract.

405
00:25:33.978 --> 00:25:35.917
Why do you intrude my privacy?

406
00:25:37.048 --> 00:25:39.048
I'm glad you mentioned it.

407
00:25:39.087 --> 00:25:41.258
You know what you wrote on the contract, right?

408
00:25:45.528 --> 00:25:47.798
Here. Do you call this your privacy?

409
00:25:49.798 --> 00:25:52.528
What's this? It's strange.

410
00:25:53.167 --> 00:25:56.137
Where did you learn this bad habit of backing out?

411
00:25:57.038 --> 00:25:58.308
Let's see.

412
00:25:58.468 --> 00:26:02.107
"Two-year Term Lease Marriage Agreement".

413
00:26:02.177 --> 00:26:03.637
What's this?

414
00:26:06.077 --> 00:26:07.647
What's this?

415
00:26:09.077 --> 00:26:11.117
(Dating Agreement)

416
00:26:13.188 --> 00:26:14.758
(Woo Soo Ji, Ma Sang Goo)

417
00:26:35.538 --> 00:26:36.637
Ji Ho.

418
00:26:38.248 --> 00:26:39.548
Take a look at this.

419
00:26:39.808 --> 00:26:42.548
What's this? "Dating Agreement"?

420
00:26:42.647 --> 00:26:46.317
Yes, this seems to be the dating agreement between Mr. Ma and Soo Ji.

421
00:26:47.248 --> 00:26:48.417
I told you...

422
00:26:48.587 --> 00:26:50.887
that they don't look good together at all.

423
00:26:52.327 --> 00:26:54.127
And look here.

424
00:26:54.758 --> 00:26:57.097
Soo Ji is the former,

425
00:26:58.268 --> 00:26:59.327
and Mr. Ma is the latter.

426
00:26:59.397 --> 00:27:01.468
Goodness, so it's real.

427
00:27:02.468 --> 00:27:05.907
Why did they sign a contract on their dating?

428
00:27:10.907 --> 00:27:12.907
Well, we're not in the position to say this.

429
00:27:13.847 --> 00:27:16.218
By the way, how do you have this?

430
00:27:16.577 --> 00:27:20.218
We bumped into each other a while ago. I think our stuff got mixed up,

431
00:27:20.647 --> 00:27:21.988
and it ended up in my briefcase.

432
00:27:22.657 --> 00:27:23.857
I see.

433
00:27:24.728 --> 00:27:28.157
It's not like this got switched with our agreement, is it?

434
00:27:35.798 --> 00:27:36.798
What?

435
00:27:40.538 --> 00:27:42.538
(Two-year Term Lease Marriage Agreement)

436
00:27:44.708 --> 00:27:46.607
You haven't dated him for long, but you're getting married?

437
00:27:46.778 --> 00:27:50.647
Many people get married only after 2 or 3 months after the relationship.

438
00:27:50.847 --> 00:27:53.587
Why do you keep calling him your landlord?

439
00:27:54.657 --> 00:27:55.958
Did I?

440
00:27:55.958 --> 00:27:57.927
- A part-time job? Why? - What?

441
00:27:59.127 --> 00:28:01.198
Well, I need to work in order to pay for my rent...

442
00:28:02.258 --> 00:28:05.468
I mean, our living expenses and phone bills.

443
00:28:08.567 --> 00:28:10.167
Ji Ho, this crazy brat.

444
00:28:30.927 --> 00:28:32.587
What do you have to give me this time?

445
00:28:32.927 --> 00:28:34.058
Well...

446
00:28:35.058 --> 00:28:38.897
It's the marinated crab which my mom sent me last time.

447
00:28:39.597 --> 00:28:41.798
She gave this so that I could share with everyone.

448
00:28:42.167 --> 00:28:44.367
And I forgot to give you some.

449
00:28:45.567 --> 00:28:48.577
Thanks. I should call her once.

450
00:28:48.938 --> 00:28:50.008
She's well, right?

451
00:28:50.308 --> 00:28:51.778
Of course.

452
00:28:51.778 --> 00:28:54.847
- She isn't ill or anything, is she? - Of course not.

453
00:28:55.048 --> 00:28:58.188
- What about your lease marriage? - Of course.

454
00:29:01.258 --> 00:29:02.988
You pay 250 dollars a month.

455
00:29:03.288 --> 00:29:05.857
Hey, there are not many places that cost only that amount these days.

456
00:29:06.157 --> 00:29:07.528
Soo Ji... Well...

457
00:29:07.528 --> 00:29:10.827
If you're okay with it, can I move into his house after two years?

458
00:29:11.228 --> 00:29:12.597
As his next wife.

459
00:29:12.667 --> 00:29:14.538
- Come on. - What?

460
00:29:15.298 --> 00:29:16.597
You did nothing good.

461
00:29:18.837 --> 00:29:19.968
Crazy brat.

462
00:29:21.938 --> 00:29:22.938
Crazy punk.

463
00:29:24.808 --> 00:29:26.248
Goodness.

464
00:29:29.677 --> 00:29:33.587
How did you even think about getting married though?

465
00:29:33.587 --> 00:29:36.688
We all have different ways...

466
00:29:37.157 --> 00:29:38.728
to live our lives.

467
00:29:38.728 --> 00:29:40.958
But you did it just for your house.

468
00:29:41.458 --> 00:29:43.427
You just did it just to get the rental fee!

469
00:29:49.998 --> 00:29:51.508
It's not just for the house.

470
00:29:53.167 --> 00:29:54.577
It's not just to get the rental fee.

471
00:29:55.208 --> 00:29:57.177
You have no idea how important the house is.

472
00:29:57.948 --> 00:29:59.048
You should also know...

473
00:30:00.308 --> 00:30:01.917
money really matters too.

474
00:30:07.657 --> 00:30:09.617
It was just an empty room to me.

475
00:30:11.258 --> 00:30:13.288
However, it was something she really needed.

476
00:30:13.827 --> 00:30:15.627
She was desperate to have her own room.

477
00:30:17.298 --> 00:30:18.667
So I shared my place...

478
00:30:19.228 --> 00:30:21.067
using the proper legal system.

479
00:30:22.038 --> 00:30:23.137
I...

480
00:30:24.367 --> 00:30:25.837
needed some money too.

481
00:30:32.208 --> 00:30:33.907
Did Ji Ho...

482
00:30:37.948 --> 00:30:39.817
remind you of her?

483
00:30:57.567 --> 00:30:59.268
I'm sorry I couldn't tell you...

484
00:31:00.038 --> 00:31:01.508
that my marriage wasn't real.

485
00:31:02.208 --> 00:31:04.407
Of course, you couldn't tell me.

486
00:31:04.647 --> 00:31:06.107
How could you tell me that?

487
00:31:06.448 --> 00:31:08.478
By the way, why are you sorry?

488
00:31:09.778 --> 00:31:11.248
You are the one who's suffering.

489
00:31:18.357 --> 00:31:19.657
Are you really okay?

490
00:31:20.357 --> 00:31:21.528
Of course.

491
00:31:22.258 --> 00:31:24.198
It was my decision.

492
00:31:25.298 --> 00:31:28.867
It takes a long time to decide something,

493
00:31:29.968 --> 00:31:33.607
but when I do, I hardly regret my decision.

494
00:31:35.137 --> 00:31:37.077
It doesn't look nothing to me.

495
00:31:38.647 --> 00:31:40.048
Your marriage...

496
00:31:41.278 --> 00:31:43.278
