500
00:31:57.897 --> 00:31:59.067
What do you mean?

501
00:31:59.067 --> 00:32:00.498
Who is that?

502
00:32:01.397 --> 00:32:02.567
My husband.

503
00:32:05.508 --> 00:32:07.407
I don't think you felt that way at first.

504
00:32:08.637 --> 00:32:10.508
Have you been falling for him while living together?

505
00:32:16.518 --> 00:32:17.647
No, it's not.

506
00:32:19.218 --> 00:32:20.718
Maybe I liked him from the start.

507
00:32:24.488 --> 00:32:27.458
I don't know when I started to feel this way.

508
00:32:29.927 --> 00:32:31.097
What about him?

509
00:32:32.698 --> 00:32:35.498
Does he like you too?

510
00:32:42.008 --> 00:32:43.137
No.

511
00:32:45.147 --> 00:32:46.978
