512
00:32:49.048 --> 00:32:50.778
that I like him.

513
00:33:07.798 --> 00:33:09.038
There must be a way...

514
00:33:10.298 --> 00:33:12.337
to reach someone's heart.

515
00:33:21.677 --> 00:33:23.117
If there's a way,

516
00:33:23.278 --> 00:33:24.587
