517
00:33:24.587 --> 00:33:28.058
there must be...

518
00:33:29.087 --> 00:33:30.488
where it starts.

519
00:33:30.488 --> 00:33:31.587
Ho Rang!

520
00:33:33.927 --> 00:33:35.028
Ho Rang!

521
00:33:35.927 --> 00:33:36.998
Look!

522
00:33:37.798 --> 00:33:39.397
Did you make it?

523
00:33:40.427 --> 00:33:43.468
I'll put 500 dollars in it too!

524
00:33:43.597 --> 00:33:47.038
As we promised, let's put 500 dollars a month from now on.

525
00:33:47.038 --> 00:33:49.308
When the three-year-term ends,

526
00:33:49.308 --> 00:33:50.907
