529
00:33:55.518 --> 00:33:57.817
We might end up buying a house with a front yard.

530
00:33:58.248 --> 00:33:59.748
I prefer an apartment.

531
00:34:00.857 --> 00:34:02.317
If that's what you want...

532
00:34:04.927 --> 00:34:06.458
Let's do that!

533
00:34:13.768 --> 00:34:18.108
(Shim Won Seok deposited 150 dollars.)

534
00:34:21.407 --> 00:34:25.208
(Yang Ho Rang deposited 500 dollars.)

535
00:34:38.757 --> 00:34:40.188
I'm so relieved now.

536
00:34:40.358 --> 00:34:43.657
If you are going to have kids and raise them, it's not too soon.

537
00:34:43.827 --> 00:34:47.568
Don't make my girl, Ho Rang, go through a hard time.

538
00:34:48.197 --> 00:34:49.297
I won't.

539
00:34:49.568 --> 00:34:51.907
I know you won't.

540
00:34:53.308 --> 00:34:56.077
This is for celebrating your new job.

