563
00:36:38.648 --> 00:36:40.347
I will book that too.

564
00:36:43.418 --> 00:36:46.148
Okay. Let's do that.

565
00:36:49.418 --> 00:36:51.558
Okay. Let's do that.

566
00:37:05.838 --> 00:37:09.507
Will there be a different way that starts...

567
00:37:13.177 --> 00:37:17.518
from where our hearts meet?

568
00:37:19.918 --> 00:37:22.358
But the thing I'm afraid of the most is...

569
00:37:24.427 --> 00:37:27.327
not that we have different ways,

570
00:37:30.358 --> 00:37:34.498
nor that we'll never meet on the way.

571
00:37:37.038 --> 00:37:38.568
What I'm afraid of the most is...

572
